<h1>Content Part &quot;Form&quot;</h1>
<h3>earlier &quot;email contact form&quot;</h3>

<p><strong><font color="#ff0000">Notice:<br />
This Content Part &quot;Email contact form&quot; was added with the version 1.2.<br />
Since the Release 1.2.9 this content part is renamed to &quot;form&quot;</font></strong></p><div style="margin:15px 0 0 0;padding:0;" class="spaceBeforeCP"></div><hr width="100%" size="2" />
<p>&nbsp;</p><div style="margin:0 0 15px 0;padding:0;" class="spaceAfterCP"></div><div style="margin:25px 0 0 0;padding:0;" class="spaceBeforeCP"></div><table width="112" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" align="left">
<tr><td class="image_td"><a href="content/images/3e83030966f5d7e1e5c4a8179436f4e7.png" rel="lightbox" target="_blank"><img src="content/images/e1fe6d55cc80e442122e3e7966a720b7.png" width="104" height="200" border="0" class="image_img" alt="form.png" /></a></td><td><img src="img/leer.gif" width="8" height="1" border="0" alt="" /></td></tr>
